High Performance Computing - Labs 1 to 3

Main files

- `main.cpp`: matrix kernels from Lab 1 to Lab 3
- `quad.cpp`: numerical integration benchmark for Lab 3
- `Makefile`: builds all executables from the lab root
- `include/Stopwatch.hpp`: timing helper
- `slides/submission.pdf`: final presentation PDF

Build

- `make`

Useful runs

- `./run_01_matrix_norm_novec.sh`
- `./run_02a_mmul_simple_ijk.sh`
- `./run_02b_mmul_simple_all.sh`
- `./run_03_mmul_restrict.sh`
- `./run_04_mmul_blocked.sh`
- `./run_05_mmul_simd.sh`
- `./run_06_mmul_openmp.sh`
- `./run_08_quadrature.sh`

Plotting

The Python helpers are:

- `plot_csv.py`
- `plot_quad_csv.py`
- `generate_submission_figures.py`

Local Python environment:

- `python3 -m venv .venv`
- `./.venv/bin/pip install -r requirements.txt`

Generate the figures used in the slides:

- `./.venv/bin/python generate_submission_figures.py`
